{"tid":1322651,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"英華中學24歲女教師同2個義士俾人拉冇人講?","createTime":"2019-07-16T04:07:29.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-17T08:35:38.000Z","uid":170929,"like":7,"dislike":19,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"c418bf170f88cbf6994d361c722858b1ddb5b714","tid":1322651,"uid":170929,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T04:07:29.000Z","msg":"【<a href=\"http://on.cc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fon.cc&d=SZ2g%2FZg1uDubc4iNJejiXsLrQrhaJullgCUoYOUuTa8%3D&h=452827bb\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">on.cc</a>東網專訊】上周日（7日）九龍區的反對《逃犯修訂》大遊行，市民在遊行結束後未有散去，更霸佔彌敦道，並往旺角推進。期間，一名30歲自稱營商的女子，疑因被認作是便衣女警，被其他示威者包圍，要求她刪除所拍攝影片，一名戴口罩的男子更從後將她箍住，亦有人扯她衣服，女事主翌日報警。西九龍總區重案組接手跟進，經深入調查後，今日（15日）拘捕2男一女，懷疑與案有關。<br />\n<br />\n被捕人士包括姓蘇（24歲）女子，據了解，她在香港中文大學畢業，現在英華女學校任教師。另一名被捕男子姓吳（24歲），任職保安公司職員，以及一名姓黃（31歲）男子。他們俱涉嫌襲擊致造成實際身體傷害、非法集結及非法禁錮，黃另涉非禮被捕。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />可以點幫佢地？"},{"pid":"abd5be660081a61ae6a633ca8d4af6efa458d2f4","tid":1322651,"uid":209865,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T04:08:33.000Z","msg":"出黎發夢咪幫到佢地囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4e905612caa002a76156de91e8efd7a21678afc5","tid":1322651,"uid":170929,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T04:14:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6035d5877060fe6bde4c21d7071d9132c2e6ab88","tid":1322651,"uid":280821,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T07:47:27.000Z","msg":"要吉人天相呀，係咪得大紀元影到？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"acd1ef60347324425c4f0e9e9d980826d4a42455","tid